ipt 一开始只是写网页的；后来写应用、写服务端、写桌面；现在连 Web Server 配置都能写了。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(90, 90, 90);font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-align: left;text-indent: 0em;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从 Node 到 Deno 到 Bun，再到 njs + QuickJS，</span><strong style=\"border-right-style:none;background-size:auto;border-top-width:3px;border-bottom-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);background-attachment:scroll;font-weight:bold;padding-left:0px;border-left-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-left:0px;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-position-x:0%;background-position-y:0%;border-left-style:none;border-top-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-left-radius:0px;margin-top:0px;border-bottom-right-radius:0px;background-image:none;height:auto;padding-top:0px;border-bottom-left-radius:0px;border-right-width:3px;padding-bottom:0px;border-right-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-top-right-radius:0px;border-left-width:3px;border-top-style:none;margin-right:0px;background-clip:border-box;width:auto;border-bottom-width:3px;border-bottom-style:none;background-origin:padding-box;margin-bottom:0px;padding-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">JS 正在成为“写啥都行”的万能胶水语言</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(90, 90, 90);font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-align: left;text-indent: 0em;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这一次，它没试图取代什么，只是在最不起眼的角落，把事情做得更顺、更灵活、更现代。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(90, 90, 90);font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-align: left;text-indent: 0em;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-to